Background
 This Request for Information (RFI) is issued by the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers to identify vendors capable of providing data management tools and support services for Formerly Used Defense Sites (FUDS) Chemical (FUDSChem) data. 
The goal of this contract is to enhance environmental management systems and ensure compliance with mission essential items related to environmental management.

Work Details
 The contractor will be responsible for the following tasks: 
1. Project Management; 
2. Maintenance and Enhancement of FUDSChem; 
3. Additional Enhancement of FUDSChem (Optional);
